(181, 'MYSTERION', 'http://books.google.com/books/content?id=_A5CDwAAQBAJ&printsec=frontcover&img=1&zoom=5&edge=curl&source=gbs_api', 'In a time where violent heretic hunting occurred, a secret society called the Rose Cross, who practiced Alchemy, were under oppression for being blasphemous. The Alchemist Leon rewrote his own memory and was living his life as a completely different person. The Philosopher\'s Stone, homunculus, and the secrets of his past are about to be revealed...! ...', 28, '2013-08-01', NULL, 117, 2),
